Package: rflexscan
Type: Package
Title: Tools and Methods to Analyze Spatial Count Data Using the Flexible
    Spatial Scan Statistic
Version: 0.1
Date: 2019-04-15
Author: Takahiro Otani,
    Kunihiko Takahashi
Maintainer: Takahiro Otani <otani@med.nagoya-u.ac.jp>
Description: The FleXScan (https://sites.google.com/site/flexscansoftware/home)
    is a software to analyze spatial count data. The rflexscan package provides
    functions for running FleXScan on R.
